{"confidence": "Low", "created_at": "2026-07-04T00:32:17+00:00", "domains": ["AI Project"], "entry_count": 1, "id": "PAT-7D1472B6E8E157D2", "last_entry_id": "IA-20260704003217-2A1348", "metadata": {}, "pattern": "Polymath intelligence is not wide knowledge \u2014 it is deep routing that transfers cheaply. One well-understood domain becomes a universal routing template. Master a routing structure deeply in one domain, then map it to every adjacent domain.", "tags": ["ai project", "analogy", "transfer", "polymath", "routing", "learning", "mental-model", "fitness"], "updated_at": "2026-07-04T00:32:17+00:00"}
{"confidence": "Low", "created_at": "2026-07-04T00:32:17+00:00", "domains": ["Lab"], "entry_count": 1, "id": "PAT-4DE6C2089A83556B", "last_entry_id": "IA-20260704003217-F849EE", "metadata": {}, "pattern": "Measurement converts opinion into routing signal. Every domain running on feeling instead of data is running on a degraded map. Add one measurement to any stuck domain and the routing decision becomes obvious.", "tags": ["lab", "data", "measurement", "signal", "fitness", "sales", "routing", "proof", "customer"], "updated_at": "2026-07-04T00:32:17+00:00"}
{"confidence": "Low", "created_at": "2026-07-04T00:32:17+00:00", "domains": ["AI Project"], "entry_count": 1, "id": "PAT-E5630A8F9D4D595C", "last_entry_id": "IA-20260704003217-E2ADA6", "metadata": {}, "pattern": "All learning systems improve by the same mechanism: collect data, detect patterns, correct models, route better. The constraint is always the same: no feedback = no improvement.", "tags": ["ai project", "routing", "analogy", "ai", "human-intelligence", "feedback", "result", "info-analyzer", "training", "operator", "pattern"], "updated_at": "2026-07-04T00:32:17+00:00"}
